1
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:14,760
The video can't be restored

2
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:16,040
Just make do with the audio

3
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,080
Doctor, my wife, she...

4
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:23,080
Her stomach hurts really bad

5
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:24,080
Do you want to come take a look?

6
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,960
Okay, okay, this is all normal

7
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:27,000
Thank you, doctor

8
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,840
It's just the sound of a patient visiting

9
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,800
Nothing strange about it

10
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:43,960
The hospital was closed

11
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:52,080
Wait a minute

12
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:53,480
What is this part?

13
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:55,000
Here, here

14
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,120
Right here

15
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,280
Amplify it, amplify it

16
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,000
It hurts!

17
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,320
Amplify this part a bit more

18
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:13,840
Can't boost it anymore

19
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,920
The audio is already distorted

20
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:27,640
No

21
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:29,200
This... that's it?

22
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,680
What else did you expect?

23
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:36,040
The sound of the killer committing the crime

24
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,920
There can't be no sound at all, right?

25
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:41,280
The killer struck in the examination room

26
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,400
It's normal that nothing was recorded

27
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,960
Then there's only that sound from just now

28
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,920
It's a bit strange

29
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,440
What is it?

30
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:03,760
Shen Man

31
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,400
Since this incident came out

32
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,920
our video account has gone viral, look

33
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,120
Followers have already passed one million

34
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:10,760
Shen Man

35
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:13,040
The task you gave me before

36
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,400
I did a pretty good job, right?

37
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:18,800
Not bad

38
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,520
I'll treat you tonight

39
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:21,160
Okay

40
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:21,920
Is anyone here?

41
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:25,240
You must be Shen Man

42
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,880
Your place is really hard to find

43
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:31,520
Got any water?

44
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,080
You're looking for me?

45
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:47,040
I am...

46
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,160
a cleaner at Ruize Private Hospital

47
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,880
I have a lot of inside info

48
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:53,360
Your video account is so hot right now

49
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:54,800
Do you want to consider

50
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:57,480
releasing some more explosive news?

51
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,360
Related to Dr. Ai Xia

52
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,440
Then tell me about it

53
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,760
This case is so popular right now

54
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:29,040
I can sell this info to anyone

55
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,160
Give me some more

56
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,240
Now can you tell me?

57
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:50,640
On the day of the crime

58
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,560
someone argued with Dr. Ai Xia

59
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,640
How do you know?

60
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,640
I was there when they were arguing

61
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,880
You insist on making a scene, don't you?

62
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:02,360
I advise you to think about the consequences

63
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,440
That person...

64
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:17,480
looked a lot like Dr. Sang Tuo

65
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:18,800
Dr. Sang Tuo?

66
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,400
Why didn't you tell the police this?

67
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:26,840
Tell the police?

68
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:30,080
Might just bring trouble on myself

69
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,640
Telling you...

70
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,720
I can make some extra cash

71
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:37,520
I'm off

72
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,840
Get me another bottle of water

73
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:43,400
Okay

74
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:07,840
Jiang Li

75
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,160
I have an important lead

76
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,760
Dr. Sang Tuo from Ruize Private Hospital

77
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,040
is very likely a suspect

78
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:14,640
He's dead

79
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,280
What?

80
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:05,920
And this.

81
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,080
Another one dead.

82
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,080
Now we're in trouble.

83
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:18,840
Looking at the MO,

84
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:20,360
it's likely the same killer.

85
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,280
Another one dead.

86
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:26,120
The selection for Tuo Cheng's Best Police Station

87
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,080
is this month.

88
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:28,840
If we don't find the killer soon,

89
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,760
the team leader is going to yell at us again.

90
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,960
The method used to kill Ai Xia before

91
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,040
is almost identical.

92
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,040
First, control the victim with anesthetics,

93
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:43,080
then cut off the victim's genitals,

94
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,040
then use blood

95
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:45,840
to write occult incantations on the body.

96
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:47,280
The murder weapon,

97
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,360
the Demon Idol,

98
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,960
and the patterns on the Demon Idol...

99
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,680
This matches Ai Xia's crime scene

100
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,400
exactly.

101
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:54,160
I don't think this killer is human.

102
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,920
This is a supernatural event.

103
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:29,600
That occult art Zan-what's-his-name mentioned last time,

104
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,360
I went back and checked.

105
00:08:32,160 --> 00:08:34,080
Although the incantations on Sang Tuo's body

106
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,200
are different from Ai Xia's,

107
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,520
the occult art used on them

108
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:37,400
is consistent.

109
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,840
It's just that

110
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:41,080
it differs between men and women.

111
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:46,640
It seems the killer hated both victims intensely.

112
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,160
The demon represents the deceased.

113
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,400
Killing them with a Demon-Slaying Pestle

114
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,280
is an act of exorcism.

115
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,720
This is revenge.

116
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,160
What the hell is this weather.

117
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,200
What is it?

118
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:09,200
So what can you hear from this sound?

119
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:12,360
Don't you think the crime scene

120
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:14,040
in Dr. Ai Xia's office

121
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:15,480
was missing something?

122
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,440
What thing?

123
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:21,720
Ai Xia's uterus.

124
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:31,960
It's the kneeling cushion in front of the shrine.

125
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,880
Forensic Examiner Pa Xin said

126
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:38,800
Ai Xia was administered anesthetic before death.

127
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,720
But there were no needle marks on the body,

128
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,480
and no drug residue in the stomach.

129
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,240
Around the mouth and nose,

130
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,840
there were no signs of forced inhalation.

131
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,840
Then how did the killer

132
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,120
make her inhale the anesthetic?

133
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:52,360
The killer hid the anesthetic in the kneeling cushion.

134
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:54,840
That's what I thought too.

135
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,080
Come in.

136
00:10:58,680 --> 00:10:59,200
Chief.

137
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,480
The test report is out.

138
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,960
With Shen Man's phone,

139
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:07,960
the stuff dug out with it was fiber.

140
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:10,840
It's residue from the kneeling cushion.

141
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,960
The killer took the kneeling cushion too,

142
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,680
burned and buried it,

143
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,720
because they didn't want us to detect

144
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,000
traces of the anesthetic residue.

145
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:23,720
So this sound is when Ai Xia was kneeling

146
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:24,960
and rubbing against the kneeling cushion.

147
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,240
So what does this prove?

148
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,840
It proves the killer knew Ai Xia well.

149
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,440
He knew Ai Xia's habits very well.

150
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:32,320
Not only knew her habits,

151
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,720
but also used anesthetic drugs.

152
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:34,920
Both victims

153
00:11:34,920 --> 00:11:36,800
were doctors at Ruize Private Hospital.

154
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,520
The killer is very likely

155
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:39,640
someone from inside the hospital.

156
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,680
Shen Man said

157
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:42,600
the incantations,

158
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,000
the Demon-Slaying Pestle,

159
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,120
the Demon Idol,

160
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,560
show that the killer is seeking revenge.

161
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,720
The killer very likely

162
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,600
had a grudge against both Ai Xia and Sang Tuo.

163
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,080
But for these things,

164
00:11:53,800 --> 00:11:54,960
we still need to go back inside the hospital

165
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,720
and ask around.

166
00:11:56,800 --> 00:11:57,480
Wait a second.

167
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,480
I have a question.

168
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:01,480
These two consecutive victims

169
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:03,560
are both doctors at Ruize Private Hospital.

170
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:05,520
It has now seriously affected

171
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:06,480
their business.

172
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:08,200
After all, it is a private hospital.

173
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:10,120
And I also heard the hospital

174
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,880
has secretly issued a gag order.

175
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:14,960
Any negative news about the hospital

176
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:17,120
is strictly forbidden from being revealed to the police.

177
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,080
If anyone is caught,

178
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,240
they will be fired immediately.

179
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,200
Someone has a way.

180
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,720
How did you find this place?

181
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,120
I want to ask you something.

182
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,840
Do you know if anyone in this hospital

183
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:49,320
had a grudge against both Ai Xia and Sang Tuo?

184
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:56,720
I just want to know some inside scoop.

185
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,840
Turn it into a story.

186
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,200
Post it on my account.

187
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:00,600
And get another wave of traffic.

188
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,080
As for the hospital...

189
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,120
Just pretend you don't know.

190
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,200
You make money.

191
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,200
I get traffic.

192
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:05,840
Isn't that great?

193
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,720
It's not about the money.

194
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,720
If the hospital finds out...

195
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,360
I could lose my job.

196
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:35,720
Then this money... money...

197
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,720
Speaking of grudges...

198
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,120
I do recall someone.

199
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:45,880
Anna.

200
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,600
Lanatoside C injection, 2ml.

201
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:48,680
Quick.

202
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:49,880
Exhale.

203
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:51,200
Relax.

204
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,120
Relax.

205
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,360
Good, very good.

206
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:54,880
When I tell you to push...

207
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:55,800
...that's when you push.

208
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:56,720
Inhale.

209
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,600
Then hold your breath.

210
00:13:58,600 --> 00:13:59,360
Push!

211
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,080
Keep going!

212
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:02,720
One more time!

213
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:03,840
The patient is hemorrhaging!

214
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:11,480
Anna.

215
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:13,600
She used to be an intern at our hospital.

216
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:14,840
During that surgery...

217
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:16,600
She got nervous and grabbed the wrong medicine.

218
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:18,200
Causing the mother and unborn child to die.

219
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:18,840
And then?

220
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,840
Everyone else in that surgery was fine.

221
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:24,200
The hospital just fired Anna.

222
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,800
I heard...

223
00:14:25,800 --> 00:14:27,800
She even went to prison for it.

224
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:52,360
Delicious.

225
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:54,600
The surgery where Anna had the accident...

226
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:56,080
Sang Tuo and Ai Xia were both there.

227
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:57,880
Anna.

228
00:14:57,880 --> 00:14:59,600
Anna is definitely connected to the case.

229
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,320
Right.

230
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:12,800
Officer Mei Dong.

231
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,000
Check something for me.

232
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:15,200
About...

233
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:20,840
A medical malpractice incident three years ago.

234
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,680
A pregnant woman hemorrhaged during a difficult birth.

235
00:15:22,680 --> 00:15:23,840
And didn't make it.

236
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:25,080
Sang Tuo and Ai Xia...

237
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,440
...both participated in that surgery.

238
00:15:26,800 --> 00:15:28,080
Check who else was present.

239
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,120
Also...

240
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:30,840
Anna is a major suspect.

241
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:32,080
Hey, rookie.

242
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,360
Why don't you be the team leader?

243
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:34,720
You just got here...

244
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:36,560
And you're bossing everyone around.

245
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:38,200
If there's a lead, we have to investigate.

246
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:39,360
Why so much nonsense?

247
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:52,320
You...

248
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,360
This kind of...

249
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:14,280
Sedative hypnotic medication.

250
00:16:14,280 --> 00:16:15,360
You should take less of it.

251
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:16,920
The side effects are too strong.

252
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:19,000
Taking too much makes it harder to sleep.

253
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:23,360
After Shen Qing was gone...

254
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:26,080
It has been a bit tough.

255
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:40,880
Hello?

256
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,040
Okay.

257
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:50,320
I have to go back to the station.

258
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:52,080
I'll just...

259
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:52,880
...head out first.

260
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:58,960
Jiang Li. Shen Man.

261
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:03,880
You... you say...

262
00:17:24,080 --> 00:17:25,480
Got it free with a phone top-up.

263
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:31,480
Thanks.

264
00:17:32,360 --> 00:17:33,480
Just now...

265
00:17:33,720 --> 00:17:35,000
Why did you call me?

266
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:48,120
There's a grain of rice on your face.

267
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:00,120
Thanks.

268
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:02,960
Bye.

269
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:11,000
Why didn't you say so earlier?

270
00:18:25,520 --> 00:18:26,120
Hello?

271
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:27,280
Jiang Li.

272
00:18:27,760 --> 00:18:29,040
Anna isn't the killer.

273
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:31,840
She's already dead.

274
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:34,200
I've sent the cemetery location...

275
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:35,040
...to you.
